{
  "stem": "22582.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't know, a pyre, you know, when they put one layer of wood, then one layer, or after they brought them, and they shot them, one layer of, you know, of people, of-- of dead people.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the fire was going on as long as I remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "For-- it was sitting there from, I don't know, October, I believe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I think October, till we left the-- the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was always fire going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It would smell the-- the flesh.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto, [INAUDIBLE] Polish police on the outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was-- and there's supposed to be a Jewish police inside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But outside is Polish police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And naturally, it was so we had a commander, a guy who was actually a peasant.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was in charge of the-- of the-- of the German police, sort of.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And gestapo was coming every day, almost every day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't know what kind of business they had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And usually, they shot a few people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or-- or-- or they look for somebody, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Or if they needed something, or they [? leave ?] any directives, they-- they were coming.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and that's what it-- everybody had to be on the toe all the time, because we never knew when it's going-- somebody is going to come.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Falkman, ?] at that time, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Falkman. ?] And another one was, how do you call?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I forgot the name already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, but they had to do what they were told.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, there's nothing, nothing they could do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, they-- they put up, I don't  know, if they wanted to be or not, whatever they, or what was the reason why they were, but they had to do whatever they were told.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
